        "text": "New Anthropic Fellows research: Model Spec Midtraining (MSM).\n\nStandard alignment methods train AIs on examples of desired behavior. But this can fail to generalize to new situations.\n\nMSM addresses this by first teaching AIs how we would like them to generalize and why.",
        "url": "https://twitter.com/AnthropicAI/status/2051758528562364902",
        "time": "7h",
        "replies": 75,
        "retweets": 126,
        "likes": 0,
        "summary": "Anthropic新研究：模型训练中期规范（MSM）解决AI泛化问题。",
        "key_data": [
